# CLIP Changelog for sys-auth/pam_pkcs11

*pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r7 (07 Aug 2014)

  07 Aug 2014; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r7.ebuild, -pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r6.ebuild,
  files/pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-clip-label.patch:
  Fix previous edit where config file was added twice to the structure. (build
  failure on amd64 but silent on 32b arches)

*pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r6 (12 Feb 2014)

  12 Feb 2014; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r6.ebuild, -pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r5.ebuild:
  pam_pkcs11.conf has moved to /var/run/

*pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r5 (11 Feb 2014)

  11 Feb 2014; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r5.ebuild, -pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r4.ebuild:
  pam_pkcs11.conf is not part of this package anymore.

*pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r4 (11 Feb 2014)

  11 Feb 2014; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r4.ebuild, -pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r3.ebuild:
  Fixed bug in key selection during signature.

  22 Jan 2014; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  files/pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-clip-label.patch:
  Remove relative paths ('..') from patch, those are no longer
  supported with the latest eutils.

*pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r3 (28 Mar 2013)

  28 Mar 2013; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r3.ebuild, -pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r2.ebuild:
  Remove threads use (conflicts with libgtop11dotnet and
  p11proxy filter).
  Changed expected certificate label.

*pam_pkcs11-0.6.3-r1 (24 Oct 2012)

