*pam_pkcs11-0.6.2-r5 (14 Jan 2011)

  14 Jan 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pam_pkcs11-0.6.2-r5.ebuild, -pam_pkcs11-0.6.2-r4.ebuild,
  files/clip_pam_pkcs11.conf:
  Move the ca/crl path to /etc/admin.
  Remove verictl2 eclass (no longer used) and move install
  commands from pkg_predeb to src_install where they belong.

*pam_pkcs11-0.6.2-r4 (17 Dec 2010)

  17 Dec 2010; Benjamin Morin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pam_pkcs11-0.6.2-r4.ebuild, -pam_pkcs11-0.6.2-r3.ebuild,
  files/clip_pam_pkcs11.conf:
  Removed the empty_mapper_file (irrelevant) and modified the
  location of the mapper file in configuration file

*pam_pkcs11-0.6.2-r3 (01 Dec 2010)

  01 Dec 2010; Benjamin Morin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pam_pkcs11-0.6.2-r3.ebuild, -pam_pkcs11-0.6.2-r2.ebuild:
  Modified the mapper used in the configuration file ;
  Added a patch to support label=xxxx to select the certificate
  to be used for signature.

*pam_pkcs11-0.6.2-r2 (10 Nov 2010)

  10 Nov 2010; Benjamin Morin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +pam_pkcs11-0.6.2-r2.ebuild, -pam_pkcs11-0.6.2-r1.ebuild:
  Replaced the pkcs11 module used in the pam configuration
  files to use the p11 proxy.

*pam_pkcs11-0.6.2-r1 (13 Jul 2010)

